元，虚增利润总额约 3900 万元，占当年利润总额的 17.78%。 2020 年虚增营业收入约 24.8 亿元，占当年营业收入的 36.47%；虚增成本约 24.4 亿元，虚增利润总额约 4416 万元，占当年利润总额的 18.30%。2021 年虚增营业收入约 7511 万元，占当年营业收入的 2.56%；虚增利润总额 7511 万元，占当年利润总额的 47.85%。四年合计虚增收入逾 86 亿元。超 9.6 万户股东懵了！这家上市公司 4 年虚增收入逾 86 亿元！监管层出手：重罚 2300 万元，下周「戴帽」 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8c0cf8588d4f8b23d91fa6384fe58902_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657814016"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrZWe2NLRhLopEAMaCTEwODQ1ODc0OSDs++myBjAAOElAEHIJNjU3ODE0MDE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1717280217.217851", "card_id": "Q_656078582", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么说韶音新出的骨传导游泳耳机 OpenSwim Pro 下水后音质一绝，堪比水下音乐厅？有用过的吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f2ca3c6d785cd00fa9b0d869782e910_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656078582"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrZWe2NLRhLopEAMaCTEwODA3MzAzMyC8wpGyBjAAOEBAEXIJNjU2MDc4NTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1717280217.218089", "card_id": "Q_657830613", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "沙王杯决赛利雅得胜利输球，C 罗跪地痛哭，如何评价他的这一举动？球星们应该如何面对逆境？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d2a68ff246eb6e739d8111dd73643552_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.co