，加班费也会严格按分钟来计算； 3. 有应届生担心自己学历能力不足，无法胜任，企业们便放低门槛，表示来应聘的「文理均可」，即便你零基础，也会对你进行充分的培训。 上周五，日本公布了今年的大学生就业率，98.1%，是自 1997 年以来的最高水平。 多家日媒称：日本这个国家，正在经历可能会持续数年的就业「超级卖方市场」。从数据上来看，日本如今的毕业生们算是赶上了最好的时候。 生育率暴跌 10 年，日本结束「内卷时代」_ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-17100fa191b1543969a7d31ee53e2c41_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657770277"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIrZWe2NLRhLopEAMaCTEwODQ0ODk4MSDKouayBjAAOKsKQCVyCTY1Nzc3MDI3N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1717280217.225632", "card_id": "Q_657831784", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 64}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "看完亚历克斯·加兰执导的电影《美国内战》你有什么感受？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5969d6c7b4fd7d9a34cc19df4f925f9e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "31 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657831784"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrZWe2NLRhLopEAMaCTEwODQ2MjY4MyCEh+uyBjAAOHVAJnIJNjU3ODMxNzg0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1717280217.225957", "card_id": "Q_657567666", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 120}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么工作很努力，却得不到上级的青睐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "职场上，是否遇到这样的情况: 论工作，自己很敬业，很认真，很用心，可是总是入不了领导法眼，加班领导总是看不了，开会总上不了主桌，陪领导吃饭总没有自己的份；论人品，礼贤下士，谦让谦虚有佳，可是领导总是看不了。这样的情况导致个人总是一百分的努力，得不到一百分的回报，怎么办？是继续坚持，还是放弃躺平？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/f25303335_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link